This uses two methods to calculate Pi:

Randomized Points, explained here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fQo2B3kFYm4

Polygons, explained here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D09r1lH_Sow


You need to install pygame (www.pygame.org) and python 2 (https://www.python.org/download/)

Python3 will not work with this application.